# Runtime data (Postgres + mail volumes) lives inside the stack dir — never build-context
# it. `data` only matches the context root; `**/data` also catches deploy/data in the
# portable template (build context = repo root), whose mail-state is root-owned and
# unreadable, which would otherwise break `docker compose build` on any rebuild.
